tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE car_models (
  model_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  model_name TEXT,
  production_year INT,
  manufacturer_id INT,
  FOREIGN KEY (manufacturer_id) REFERENCES car_manufacturers(manufacturer_id)
);

CREATE TABLE car_manufacturers (
 manufacturer_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
 manufacturer_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL
)

CREATE TABLE cars (
    car_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    model_id INT,
    year_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (model_id) REFERENCES car_models(model_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (year_id) REFERENCES production_years(year_id)
);
